snippet.title: Funny World Quiz - Weltraumerei - Trivia game for Android
snippet.description:
This is a challenging trivia game for Android with fun facts questions about what each country is famous for. Most topics are about culture, natural wonders, world records, strangle laws, curious things in politics and history and a little bit geography. It is NOT like the simple geography questions in many other apps. 

Available in the Google Play Store (Beta)
http://www.weltraumerei.com
